body: BUILTIN(ArrayPop) and GenericArrayPop in builtins/builtins-array.cc — GenericArrayPop handles ToObject, ToLength, Get, DeletePropertyOrElement, Set length and returns element. Builtin wrapper BUITIN(ArrayPop) checks IsJSArrayWithExtensibleFastElements and either uses ElementsAccessor::ForKind(...)->Pop or falls back to GenericArrayPop. Code lines: builtins/builtins-array.cc (GenericArrayPop and BUILTIN(ArrayPop))
explanation: This is the generic/slow path implementation of Array.pop that handles non-fast arrays and proxies; the BUILTIN(ArrayPop) entry is the target for the TF TailCallJSBuiltin fallback.
